%section#page
  .row
    .large-12.columns
      %h1
        About Us
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        What is Nooga Startups?
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %p
            Nooga Startups is a directory of the awesome startups located in Chattanooga, Tennessee and was inspired by
            %a{href: "http://wearemadeinny.com/"}Made in New York.
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        Chatta-what?
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %p
            Chattanooga fondly known as the 'Noog, 'Nooga, or simply "The Paris of Southeast." Chattanooga is home to a number of great startups, a fantastic outdoor scene, delicious food, and some great whiskey.
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        Interesting facts about Chattanooga:
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %ul
            %li The world's first coca-cola bottling plant opened here in 1899.
            %li The annual Riverbend Music Festival is consistently rated as one of the best festivals in the country.
            %li World-class kayaking and climbing is located within thirty minutes of the city.
            %li The country's first 1gb/s residential network, and the coverage stretches across the entire county.
            %li Conveniently located ninety minutes from Atlanta, Nashville, Birmingham, and Knoxville. From country music concerts to the world's busiest international airport... it's all close.
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        What's the point?
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %p
            It's time to get the secret out... Chattanooga has an emerging tech scene, a thriving downtown, and a lot of energy and momentum. We want to make it easier for engineers, journalists & founders to see whats happening in Chattanooga and get more information about the movement.
          %p
            Software is eating the world and the most successful economies of tomorrow are building around this. Our goal is for Chattanooga to be one of these economies and it's time to build the buzz and bring in the talent.
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        How can I get my startup on the list?
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %p
            The easieszt way is to submit a
            %a{href: "https://github.com/Tgemayel/Nooga-Startups/pulls"}pull request
            or tweet us
            %a{href: "https://twitter.com/NoogaStartups"}@NoogaStartups
            if you need help.
          %p
            When submitting your pull request, make sure your image is 600x400 to keep all images consistent in size.
          %p
            Please note that at this time we are only looking for product-focused tech startups featuring a website our users can visit to learn more.
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        New to Github?
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %p
            Please reference our
            %a{href: "https://github.com/Tgemayel/Nooga-Startups/blob/master/Readme.md#how-can-i-get-my-startup-added-to-this-list"}readme
            to get started.
  .row
    .large-10.columns{role: "content"}
      %h3
        I want to get involved
      .row
        .large-10.columns
          %p
            Great! We fully intend on this being a community run project. Check the
            %a{href: "https://github.com/Tgemayel/Nooga-Startups/issues"}issues log
            to see what things you can tackle first!
